 1994-18081994-11-010,  ,  ,  ,  ,  ,  ,  SSC
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Supply and Services of certain persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective November 1, 1994. (Ron D. Fromson, Winnipeg, Manitoba, in the place of Grant S. Holmes, who has resigned; and Timothy Spiegel, Calgary, Alberta, in the place of Gary Davidge, whose term has expired)
